entry.title: piyush0101/merge-report
entry.summary:
A svn missing merge report built with Scalatra

merge-report

Build & Run

$ cd merge-report
$ ./sbt
> container:start
> browse

If browse doesn't launch your browser, manually open http://localhost:8080/ in your browser.
